 "lines": [
  {
   "i": 1,
   "en": "Ryo"
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "Mr. Takeda, I've come to ask you again."
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "Takeda"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "What is it, Akizuki-kun?"
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "If I announce that I'm really a boy,"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "and everyone accepts me for it..."
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "would you consider giving Yumeko-chan"
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "another chance?"
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "Hmm..."
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "And, if I do succeed―㌍"
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "there's one more thing!"
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "I want you to... put me on your show,"
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "\"Old Whistle\"!"
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "Oho...!"
  },
  {
   "i": 15,
   "en": "So you're finally getting serious, hm?"
  },
  {
   "i": 16,
   "en": "Yes! I want to appear on your show"
  },
  {
   "i": 17,
   "en": "as a male idol!"
  },
  {
   "i": 18,
   "en": "Of course I'd welcome you singing as"
  },
  {
   "i": 19,
   "en": "your true self, without any lies..."
  },
  {
   "i": 20,
   "en": "But that alone isn't enough"
  },
  {
   "i": 21,
   "en": "to make me say yes."
  },
  {
   "i": 22,
   "en": "Huh?"
  },
  {
   "i": 23,
   "en": "Not unless you awaken that true power"
  },
  {
   "i": 24,
   "en": "sleeping within you..."
  },
  {
   "i": 25,
   "en": "and show me you can sing even better"
  },
  {
   "i": 26,
   "en": "than you ever have before."
  },
  {
   "i": 27,
   "en": "Urk... That's true, I suppose."
  },
  {
   "i": 28,
   "en": "So, I'm going to set you a challenge."
  },
  {
   "i": 29,
   "en": "There is a festival called Idol"
  },
  {
   "i": 30,
   "en": "Ultimate, the pinnacle of idol events."
  },
  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "After you announce you're a boy, you'll"
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "take on the audition for a spot in it."
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "As a male idol, of course."
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
   "en": "So if I get results there..."
  },
  {
   "i": 35,
   "en": "I mean, if I win..."
  },
  {
   "i": 36,
   "en": "Right. I'll offer you a spot on"
  },
  {
   "i": 37,
   "en": "Old Whistle, and..."
  },
  {
   "i": 38,
   "en": "I'll be able to reconsider"
  },
  {
   "i": 39,
   "en": "Sakurai-kun myself, too."
  },
  {
   "i": 40,
   "en": "As I said before, I do admit"
  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "there's a spark in her singing."
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "Thank you so much!"
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "It's too early for thanks."
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "Oh, right! It's not like I've"
  },
  {
   "i": 45,
   "en": "won the audition yet."
  },
  {
   "i": 46,
   "en": "True, but there's one thing"
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "you mustn't forget."
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "Your mission―㌍it lies beyond"
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "being accepted as a male idol."
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "Beyond that..."
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "You know, Akizuki-kun... Lately, the"
  },
  {
   "i": 52,
   "en": "hit charts make me feel something."
  },
  {
   "i": 53,
   "en": "Feel something?"
  },
  {
   "i": 54,
   "en": "These days, the charts are filled with"
  },
  {
   "i": 55,
   "en": "artists supported only by women."
  },
  {
   "i": 56,
   "en": "By women?"
  },
  {
   "i": 57,
   "en": "Yes. Male idols backed by female fans,"
  },
  {
   "i": 58,
   "en": "female idols backed by female fans..."
  },
  {
   "i": 59,
   "en": "Something about that"
  },
  {
   "i": 60,
   "en": "feels lonely to me..."
  },
  {
   "i": 61,
   "en": "Don't you think there should be one"
  },
  {
   "i": 62,
   "en": "loved by both men and women alike?"
  },
  {
   "i": 63,
   "en": "Songs that everyone hums along to"
  },
  {
   "i": 64,
   "en": "and talks about together..."
  },
  {
   "i": 65,
   "en": "I want to usher in"
  },
  {
   "i": 66,
   "en": "a happy era like that."
  },
  {
   "i": 67,
   "en": "And you want... me to create it?"
  },
  {
   "i": 68,
   "en": "Yes. No one else can."
  },
  {
   "i": 69,
   "en": "Your voice... it has both"
  },
  {
   "i": 70,
   "en": "strength and sweetness."
  },
  {
   "i": 71,
   "en": "Only you can sing songs that reach"
  },
  {
   "i": 72,
   "en": "the hearts of men and women alike."
  },
  {
   "i": 73,
   "en": "For a new era of song... awaken that"
  },
  {
   "i": 74,
   "en": "power and win the audition."
  },
  {
   "i": 75,
   "en": "U-Understood!"
  },
  {
   "i": 76,
   "en": "I'll give it everything I've got!"
  },
  {
   "i": 77,
   "en": "...So when will you announce to the"
  },
  {
   "i": 78,
   "en": "nation that you're a boy?"
  },
  {
   "i": 79,
   "en": "It'll be soon, on a TV music show."
  },
  {
   "i": 80,
   "en": "I see..."
  },
  {
   "i": 81,
   "en": "No doubt―㌍it'll stir up a storm."
  },
  {
   "i": 82,
   "en": "...I'm sure it will."
  },
  {
   "i": 83,
   "en": "But that's just what I want!"
  },
  {
   "i": 84,
   "en": "The future I'm aiming for"
  },
  {
   "i": 85,
   "en": "lies beyond it, after all."
  },
  {
   "i": 86,
   "en": "Indeed."
  },
  {
   "i": 87,
   "en": "I'm entrusting―㌍everything to you."
  },
  {
   "i": 88,
   "en": "Yes, sir!"
  },
  {
   "i": 89,
   "en": "President"
  },
  {
   "i": 90,
   "en": "Ryo, I've already spoken with"
  },
  {
   "i": 91,
   "en": "the show's staff in advance."
  },
  {
   "i": 92,
   "en": "I told them, \"Our Ryo will have"
  },
  {
   "i": 93,
   "en": "something interesting to say on air.\""
  },
  {
   "i": 94,
   "en": "Really? Thank you so much!"
  },
  {
   "i": 95,
   "en": "The moment's finally come, hasn't it..."
  },
  {
   "i": 96,
   "en": "Yes. But are you sure?"
  },
  {
   "i": 97,
   "en": "This is your last chance to turn back."
  },
  {
   "i": 98,
   "en": "I'm not turning back."
  },
  {
   "i": 99,
   "en": "My dream, Yumeko-chan's dream, Takeda's"
  },
  {
   "i": 100,
   "en": "dream... they all rest on my shoulders!"
  },
  {
   "i": 101,
   "en": "Let's do this! My long-awaited debut"
  },
  {
   "i": 102,
   "en": "as a boy is finally heeere!"
  },
  {
   "i": 103,
   "en": "First, I've got to win over"
  },
  {
   "i": 104,
   "en": "fans all across the country!"
  }
 ]
